OL,3,CPM faces renewed calls from parliament
OL,4,Cto pass Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,7,Ftold MPs "there should be no more
OL,8,Fdelays" in creating a duty of candour
OL,9,Fin law.
OL,11,FThe Labour Government has proposed a
OL,12,Fduty of candour as part of the bill,
OL,13,Fto meet a manifesto pledge.
OL,15,FBut its progress through Parliament
OL,16,Fhas stalled amid a row over whether
OL,17,Fpeople in security services, such as
OL,18,FMI5 and MI6, would be subject to the
OL,19,Fsame duties as other public servants.
