OL,3,CPM faces renewed calls from parliament
OL,4,Cto pass Hillsborough Law
OL,6,F"The Prime Minister once said it would
OL,7,Fbe one of the first things he did in
OL,8,FNo 10.
OL,10,F"Will he finally do it now, even if
OL,11,Fit's the last thing he does?"
OL,13,FPrime Minister Sir Keir replied that
OL,14,FSir Ed's party "could have passed this
OL,15,Flaw a long time ago and saved a lot of
OL,16,Fgrief", when the Lib Dems and
OL,17,FConservatives were in government
OL,18,Ftogether between 2010 and 2015.
