OL,3,CPM faces renewed calls from parliament
OL,4,Cto pass Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FThe bill would create a duty for
OL,7,Fpublic authorities and public
OL,8,Fofficials to always act "with candour,
OL,9,Ftransparency and frankness in their
OL,10,Fdealings with inquiries and
OL,11,Finvestigations", and to flag
OL,12,Finformation to inquiry and
OL,13,Finvestigation leaders, if they think
OL,14,Fit is relevant.
OL,16,FIan Byrne, the Labour MP for Liverpool
OL,17,FWest Derby, last month said Bill
OL,18,Fsupporters and the Government were
OL,19,F"not in the same position" about how
OL,20,Fnew duties would apply to intelligence
OL,21,Fofficials.
OL,26,@pD@YOUsD@OO]{D@AOU{D@ZO]
