OL,3,CPM faces renewed calls from parliament
OL,4,Cto pass Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FHe said he hoped the Government would
OL,7,F"reflect on the amendments that we
OL,8,Fhave laid down to ensure that a duty
OL,9,Fof candour applies to every public
OL,10,Fservant, including the security
OL,11,Fservices, without impinging in any
OL,12,Fway, shape or form on national
OL,13,Fsecurity".
OL,15,FThe Bill is yet to clear the Commons
OL,16,Fand faces further scrutiny in both
OL,17,FHouses of Parliament at a later date.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@IO]
